





高等組織心理學


[回上一頁]




課程名稱：高等組織心理學


授課老師：王叢桂老師
上課時間：週一（E56）


授課班級：心碩一
上課地點：L103


授課大綱：
      目的：


瞭解此領域中主要研究主題；瞭解心理學知識及研究方法在組織領域中的應用與其限制。


作業：


1.        
      就有興趣之主題作一深度回溯報告（80％）


2.        
      課堂討論參與發言（20％）


閱讀主題：


一、情緒與組織行為:


emotion專題－


Brief, 
      A. P. (2001).  Organizational 
      Behavior and the Study of Affect: Keep Your Eyes on the Organization.  
      Organizational Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.86, 
      No.1, pp.131-139.


Brockner, 
      J., & Higgins, E. T. (2001).  Regulatory 
      Focus Theory: Implications for the Study of Emotions at Work.  
      Organizational Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.86, 
      No.1, pp.35-66.


Forgas, 
      J. P., & George, J. M. (2001).  Affective 
      Influences on Judgments and Behavior in Organizations: An Information 
      Processing Perspective.  Organizational 
      Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.86, No.1, pp.3-34.


Judge, 
      T. A., & Larsen, R. J. (2001).  Dispositional 
      Affect and Job Satisfaction: A Review and Theoretical Extension.  
      Organizational Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.86, 
      No.1, pp.67-98.


Kelly, 
      J. R., & Barsade, S. G. (2001).  Mood 
      and Emotions in Small Groups and Work Teams.  
      Organizational Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.86, 
      No.1, pp.99-130.


 


burn 
      out－


Maslach, 
      C., Schaufeli, W. B., & Leiter, M. P. (2001).  Job Burnout.  Annual 
      Review of Psychology, Vol.52, pp.397-422.


 


二、組織間衝突：


Callister, 
      R. R., & Wall, J. A., Jr. (2001).  
      Conflict Across Organizational Boundaries: Managed Care 
      Organizations Versus Health Care Providers.  
      Journal of Applied Psychology, Vol.86, No.4, pp.754-763.


Gelfand, 
      M. J., Nishii, L. H., Holcombe, K. M., Dyer, N., Ohbuchi, K. I., & 
      Fukuno, M. (2001).  Cultural 
      Influences on Cognitive Representations of Conflict: Interpretations of 
      Conflict Episodes in the United States and Japan.  
      Journal of Applied Psychology, Washington, Vol.86, Iss.6, 
      pp.1059-1074.


Rapoport, 
      A., & Au, W. T. (2001).  Bonus 
      and Penalty in Common Pool Resource Dilemmas under Uncertainty.  
      Organizational Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.85, 
      No.1, pp.135-165.


Tinsley, 
      C. H., & Brett, J. M. (2001).  Managing 
      Workplace Conflict in the United States and Hong Kong.  
      Organizational Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.85, 
      No.2, pp.360-381.


 


三、領導：


Brown, 
      S. P., Ganesan. S., & Challagalla, G. (2001).  Self-Efficacy as a Moderator of Information-Seeking 
      Effectiveness.  Journal of 
      Applied Psychology, Washington, Vol.86, Iss.5, pp.1043-1051.


Lyness, 
      K.S., Judiesch, M. K. (2001).  Are 
      Female Managers Quitters? The Relationships of Gender, Promotions, and 
      Family Leaves of Absence to Voluntary Turnover.  
      Journal of Applied Psychology, Washington, Vol.86, Iss.6, 
      pp.1167-1178.


Martell, 
      R. F. (2001).  A 
      diagnostic-ratio approach to measuring beliefs about the leadership 
      abilities of male and female managers.  
      Journal of Applied Psychology, Washington, Vol.86, Iss.6, 
      pp.1223-1231.


Russell, 
      C. J. (2001).  A Longitudinal 
      Study of Top-Level Executive Performance.  
      Journal of Applied Psychology, Vol.86, No.4, pp.560-573.


Tepper, 
      B. J., Duffy, M. K., & Shaw, J. D. (2001).  
      Personality Moderators of the Relationship Between Abusive 
      Supervision and Subordinates’ 
      Resistance.  Journal of 
      Applied Psychology, Washington, Vol.86, Iss.5, pp.974-983.


 


四、認知判斷（決策歷程）：


Mohammed, 
      S., & Ringseis, E. (2001).  Cognitine 
      Diversity and Consensus in Group Decision Making: The Role of Inputs, 
      Processes, and Outcomes.  Organizational 
      Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.85, No.2, pp.310-335.


Phillips, 
      J. M. (2001).  The Role of 
      Decision Influence and Team Performance in Member Self-Efficacy, 
      Withdrawal, Satisfaction with the Leader, and Willingness to Return.  Organizational 
      Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.84, No.1, pp.122-147.


Price, 
      K. H., Hall, T. W., Bos, K., Hunton, J.E., Lovett, S., & Tippett, M. 
      J. (2001).  Features of the 
      Value Function for Voice and Their Consisyency across Participants from 
      Four Countries: Great Britain, Mexico, The Netherlands, and the United 
      States.  Organizational 
      Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.84, No.1, pp.95-121.


Rettinger, 
      D. A., & Hastie, R. (2001).  Content 
      Effects on Decision Making.  Organizational 
      Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.85, No.2, pp.336-359.


Street, 
      M. D., Douglas, S. C., Geiger, S. W., & Martinko, M. J. (2001).  
      The Impact of Cognitive Expenditure on the Ethical Decision-Making 
      Process: The Cognitive Elaboration Model.  
      Organizational Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.86, 
      No.2, pp.256-277.


Teigen, 
      K. H. (2001).  When Equal 
      Chances = Good Chances: Verbal Probabilities and the Equiprobability 
      Effect.  Organizational 
      Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.85, No.1, pp.77-108.


 


五、公義與組織行為：


Cohen-Charash, 
      Y., & Spector, P. E. (2001).  The 
      Role of Justice in Organizations: A Meta-Analysis.  Organizational Behavior and Human Decision Processes, 
      Vol.86, No.2, pp.278-321.


Tepper, 
      B. J. (2001).  Health 
      Consequences of Organizational Injustice: Tests of Main and Interactive 
      Effects.  Organizational 
      Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.86, No.2, pp.197-215.


 


六、組織承諾：


Iverson, 
      R. D., & Deery, S. J. (2001).  Understanding 
      the “Personological” 
      Basis of Employee Withdrawal: The Influence of Affective Disposition on 
      Employee Tardiness, Early Departure, and Absenteeism.  Journal of Applied Psychology, Washington, Vol.86, Iss.5, 
      pp.856-866.


Klein, 
      H. J., Wesson, M. J., Hollenbeck, J. R., Wright, P. M., & DeShon, R. 
      P. (2001).  The Assessment of 
      Goal Commitment: A Measurement Model Meta-Analysis.  
      Organizational Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.85, 
      No.1, pp.32-55.


Maier, 
      G. W., & Brunstein, J. C. (2001).  
      The Role of Personal Work Goals in Newcomers’ 
      Job Satisfaction and Organizational Commitment: A Longitudinal Analysis.  
      Journal of Applied Psychology, Washington, Vol.86, Iss.5, 
      pp.1034-1042.


McElroy, 
      J. C., Morrow, P. C., & Rude, S. N. (2001).  Turnover and Organizational Performance: A Comparative 
      Analysis of the Effects of Voluntary, Involuntary, and Reduction-in-Force 
      Turnover.  Journal of 
      Applied Psychology, Washington, Vol.86, Iss.6, pp.1294-1299.


Rhoades, 
      L., Eisenberger, R., & Armeli, S. (2001).  
      Affective Commitment to the Organization: The Contribution of 
      Perceived Organizational Support.  Journal 
      of Applied Psychology, Washington, Vol.86, Iss.5, pp.825-836.


Rioux, 
      S. M., & Penner, L. A. (2001).  The 
      Causes of Organizational Citizenship Behavior: A Motivational Analysis.  
      Journal of Applied Psychology, Washington, Vol.86, Iss.6, 
      pp.1306-1314.


Turban, 
      D. B., Lau, C. M., Ngo, H. Y., & Chow, I. H. S. (2001).  
      Organizational Attractiveness of Firms in the People’s Republic 
      of China: A Person-Organization Fit Perspective.  
      Journal of Applied Psychology, Vol.86, No.2, pp.194-206.


 


七、訓練：


Argote, 
      L., Ingram, P., Levine, J. M., & Moreland, R. L. (2000).  
      Knowledge Transfer in Organizations: Learning from the Experience 
      of Others.  Organizational 
      Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.82, No.1, pp.1-8.


Gruenfeld, 
      D. H., Martorana, P. V., & Fan, E. T. (2000).  What Do Groups Learn from Their Worldliest Members? Direct 
      and Indirect Influence in Dynamic Teams.  
      Organizational Behavior and Human Decision Processes, Vol.82, 
      No.1, pp.45-59.


Levine, 
      J. M., Higgins, E. T., & Choi, H. (2000).  
      Development of Strategic Norms in Groups.  Organizational Behavior and Human Decision Processes, 
      Vol.82, No.1, pp.88-101.


Rulke, 
      D. L., Zaheer, S., & Anderson, M. H. (2000).  Sources of Managers’ Knowledge of Organizational capabilities.  Organizational Behavior and Human Decision Processes, 
      Vol.82, No.1, pp.134-149.


 


八、工作動機：


Bartol, 
      K. M., Durham, C. C., Poon, J. M. (2001).  
      Influence of Performance Evaluation Rating Segmentation on 
      Motivation and Fairness Perceptions.  
      Journal of Applied Psychology, Washington, Vol.86, Iss.6, 
      pp.1106-1119.


Erez, 
      A., & Judge, T. A. (2001).  Relationship 
      of Core Self-Evaluations to Goal Setting, Motivation, and Performance.  
      Journal of Applied Psychology, Washington, Vol.86, Iss.6, 
      pp.1270-1279.


 


九、研究方法：


Harrison, 
      M. I. (1994).  Diagnosing 
      organizations: methods, models, and processes, 2nd ed. (Applied 
      social research methods series; v.8).


Schwartzman, 
      H. B. (1993).  Ethnography 
      In Organizations (Qualitative research methods; v.27).


 


十、企業文化：


Ashkanasy, 
      N. M., Wilderom, C. P. M., & Peterson, M. F. (2000).  
      Handbook of organizational culture and climate.  
      Thousand Oaks: Sage Publications, Inc..


 


中文參考書籍


鄭伯壎、黃國隆、郭建志（主編）（1998）：《海峽兩岸管理系列叢書》，第一、二、四集。臺北：遠流出版公司。







其他：


本資料為學期初老師提供系辦公室之資料，僅供參考，實際正確資料，請於開學時親自到堂索取。




